title: PHOTOS: Storm impacts underway across South Georgia, Big Bend areas
text: PHOTOS AND VIDEOS: Storm tears down trees, damages structures in South Georgia, Big Bend This article will be updated throughout the day with weather photos and videos Published: May. 10, 2024 at 10:03 AM EDT|Updated: 3 hours ago TALLAHASSEE, Fla. (WCTV) - Storm impacts passed through our local counties Friday morning, causing several [power outages](https://www.wctv.tv/2024/05/10/current-power-outages-across-big-bend-south-georgia/), [school closures](https://www.wctv.tv/2024/05/09/school-closings-ahead-potential-storms/), and damage to homes and vehicles.
